 * val kotlinTimeZone = javaZoneId.toKotlinTimeZone()
 * ```
 *
 * ## Performance considerations
 *
 * - Time zone lookups are cached internally
 * - Conversion operations are generally fast
 * - Creating TimeZone instances is relatively expensive, so cache them when possible
 *
 * ```kotlin
 * // Good: Cache frequently used time zones
