 *
 * Fixed offset time zones provide simple, predictable conversions:
 * ```kotlin
 * val offset = UtcOffset(hours = 3)
 * val zone = FixedOffsetTimeZone(offset)
 * 
 * val instant = Instant.parse("2023-07-15T12:00:00Z")
 * val localTime = instant.toLocalDateTime(zone) // 2023-07-15T15:00:00
 * 
 * val backToInstant = localTime.toInstant(zone) // 2023-07-15T12:00:00Z
 * // Always unambiguous - no DST transitions to worry about
 * ```
 *
